# problem: circle
# title:   Break at an iteration, inspect KKT, then perturb the iterate live
#
# It's a real debugger, not a trace viewer: set a breakpoint, read the
# reduced-Hessian inertia, then OVERWRITE a primal variable mid-solve and
# watch the solver recover from the bad point.
b 3
c
p x
p kkt
@1.6 set x[0] 1.2
diff
c
